markets.title: Will total stablecoin supply on Solana be above $15B on Dec 31, 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If total USDC, USDT, PYUSD, and USDS supply on Solana is above 15 billion at 10:00 AM ET on Dec 31, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The total stablecoin supply is measured in USD-equivalent value as reported by Blockworks Research data dashboards. The measurement includes all stablecoins on Solana as classified by Blockworks, which typically includes USD-pegged stablecoins and excludes algorithmic stablecoins unless specifically included. Supply includes all versions on Solana: native, bridged, wrapped, and canonical.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the stablecoin supply is determined.
